name:

Run attachment `index.html` to start Photon. 

See https://github.com/ermouth/couch-photon 
repo for more details.
versions:
## 1.15.2

Added left panel / top bar switch to match wide monitors better. Vertical panel
only available for 1440px+ wide screens.

List performance is significantly improved, DB list is ok for nodes
with up to ~2â€¦3k buckets.

## 1.14.4

Added Include docs option for `/_all_docs` view, it is turned on automatically
for grid view.

Added grid (table) representation for docs lists, view and Mango queries. 
Tables are copy/pastable to Excel. 

Views now memoize their particular source code editor state, as well as 
reduce and grid settings.

## 1.12

Added ZIP dump/restore; [Delete DB] dlg now offers to re-create DB(s) after
deletion. Several JSON editor fixes and improvements. Task list grouping 
improved. TT Mono font excluded from the Photon package. 

## 1.11

Added `/_changes` feed view, added compound index stats for ddocs view.

## 1.10

Added index stats for ddocs view, a lot of slight UI improvements.

## 1.9

Added: group DB sync; Couch perf test; CouchDB v3 support. 

## 1.8

Improved JSON editor, added `/_stats` graphs.

## 1.7

Added structured diff for doc revisions.

## 1.6

New feature: editor for text-based attachments.

Added doc purge; DB view received `db/_design_docs` and `db/_local_docs` filters.

## 1.4

Added access restrictions, Photon no more starts without authorization.

## 1.2

Added in-place Erlang, JS and Mango view/index editors.

## 0.9.99

More or less usable version with all basic features. March, 2018.
